name: dfs.block.misreplication.processing.limit
description: Maximum number of blocks to process for initializing replication queues.

name: yarn.app.mapreduce.am.container.log.limit.kb
description:
The maximum size of the MRAppMaster attempt container logs in KB.
    0 disables the cap.

name: tfile.fs.input.buffer.size
description: Buffer size used for FSDataInputStream in bytes.

name: dfs.qjournal.queued-edits.limit.mb
description: Queue size in MB for quorum journal edits.

name: ipc.[port_number].decay-scheduler.metrics.top.user.count
description:
The number of top (i.e., heaviest) users to emit metric
    information about. This property applies to DecayRpcScheduler.

name: dfs.namenode.blocks.per.postponedblocks.rescan
description:
Number of blocks to rescan for each iteration of
    postponedMisreplicatedBlocks.

name: mapreduce.input.fileinputformat.split.minsize
description:
The minimum size chunk that map input should be split
  into.  Note that some file formats may have minimum split sizes that
  take priority over this setting.
